title: "GH-642: linked-test runner enters interactive init wizard before repository commands"
description: Prevent pm test --run sandbox/context preparation from invoking interactive pm init in initialized repositories; fail non-interactively with structured remediation when preparation cannot complete.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
