acceptance_criteria: "Linked non-PM repository commands start without an init prompt under schema, tracker, and auto PM context modes; non-TTY setup failures exit deterministically with structured remediation; regression coverage proves progress starts and the child command runs."
parent: pm-52eh
resolution: Linked-test sandboxes initialize with explicit non-interactive defaults and skip agent-guidance prompts.
expected_result: Repository linked tests begin execution without any interactive initialization prompt.
actual_result: "Sandbox setup called runInit without defaults, allowing TTY runs to enter the wizard before the linked command."
