comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T05:37:19.236Z",codex-root-20260722,"Duplicate-check evidence 2026-07-22: searched every pm status for interactive init wizard, linked-test sandbox initialization, tracker context, and adjacent GH-208/GH-463 lineages. No exact item exists; reused closed linked-test sandbox parent pm-52eh and related parity/remediation lineage pm-8izv and pm-6e1d. This item tracks GitHub issue #642 and remains open/unclaimed because it is documented, not part of the active context-index implementation bundle."
  "2026-07-22T16:31:11.692Z",codex-root,"Implementation start 2026-07-22: canonical all-status lineage and full metadata reviewed. This item is active in one broad SDK-backed contract correctness PR spanning strict Plan creation, registry-aware Plan relationship promotion, non-interactive linked-test execution, and unambiguous deletion outcomes. GitHub intake, public SDK/CLI/MCP parity, focused regression coverage, isolated installed-package dogfood, and exact 100/100/100/100 verification are in scope."
  "2026-07-22T17:00:29.817Z",codex-root,"Evidence: all four linked-test sandboxes initialize with explicit defaults=true and agentGuidance=skip. The packed installed CLI ran a linked node --version test to completion without an interactive wizard."
  "2026-07-22T17:23:23.491Z",codex-root,"Delivery PR: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/644 (exact implementation branch for non-interactive linked-test sandbox initialization)."
